{{DISPLAYTITLE:''Lord of Ultima''}}
'''''Lord of Ultima''''' is a browser-based, real-time strategy game set the the ''Ultima'' universe. It was developed and published on April 20, 2010 by [http://www.phenomic.de/ EA Phenomic]. It was free to play, however premium features required the purchase of [http://www.play4free.com/en/ Play4Free Funds]. It was announced that ''Lord of Ultima'' was to be shut down on May 12, 2014, however, the shut down began some time before that.

